snippet.title: WexeW MexeM (1.0) - 10,768,690 Clear
snippet.description:
New game by Zakichi inspired by Exed Exes and XexeX. Chill scoring game.

Scoring is kinda similar to Kaikan, but with a hyper mode added on top of it.
When you activate the hyper mode, the current multiplier value is locked in and you cannot increase it until you get out of hyper mode.

Get the game here:
https://zakichi.itch.io/wexew-mexem
